# 学习vpn

[固定ip](https://github.com/kylemanna/docker-openvpn/blob/master/docs/static-ips.md)

[docker安装vpn](https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-run-openvpn-in-a-docker-container-on-ubuntu-14-04?utm_source=githubreadme)

----------工具

1、管理界面
```
docker run -v $OVPN_DATA:/etc/openvpn -it --rm kylemanna/openvpn bash -l
```

2、更新

docker run  -v $OVPN_DATA:/etc/openvpn --rm kylemanna/openvpn ovpn_genconfig
